import React, { useContext } from 'react'
import { FaBars } from 'react-icons/fa'

const Home = () => {
  return
  (
    <main>
      <button className='sidebar-toggle'>
        <FaBars />
      </button>
      <button className='btn'>Show modal</button>
    </main>
  )
}

export default Home
